Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那堆意外收穫的海帶芽做的豆腐鍋後宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  加奈子君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您  隆顯姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮前同學真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也嘗嘗我的海帶芽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起餵她吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別躲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做夢一樣  非常幸福的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  乾脆不要醒來好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能睡懶覺哦  加奈子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來吧
